title: War of the Roses: She Showed Up At His Wife's Party
description: Jamie is in a relationship with a married man who says that he is leaving his wife to be with her but she wants to do War of the Roses to make sure that he's following through with what he says.  We find out a lot more about what he's doing with his marriage and things Jamie has done once we give him a call.
